&lt;h2 id="workflow-of-ai-automation-implementation"&gt;Workflow of AI Automation Implementation&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To successfully integrate AI automation into your business, it&amp;rsquo;s crucial to follow a structured workflow. Below is a simple diagram illustrating the steps involved:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code class="language-mermaid" data-lang="mermaid"&gt;graph TD;
